{"tid":1800233,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"別當一回事 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-27T15:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T15:19:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7eedd75929d9ed589a51880d39d7c6f672eae605","tid":1800233,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:13:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191227/20832074/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191227%2F20832074%2F&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=933ccd4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191227%2F20832074%2F&h=220412ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191227/20832074/</a><br />\n<br />\n別當一回事 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191227/large/1577352600_e0bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191227%2Flarge%2F1577352600_e0bd.jpg&h=fbfe031e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看到一則有趣的新聞：日前政府公佈有5名年輕公務員獲推薦到聯合國工作，「國家推送」自是得到中央信任，與國際接軌，且為月薪6萬多至10萬元之間的筍工。電視畫面所見，一眾發言腔調獨特，典型的小忠臣，前途無量。<br />\n<br />\n本來是沈悶的公告──但蘋果爆料5人中唯一女性陳莉婷，任職機電工程署工程師，其頂頭上司或是陳帆，陳帆現今當上運輸及房屋局局長了，陳莉婷就是他的姪女。二人關係應該不是秘密，因為政府需填寫「三世書」，也有品格審查，怎會不知是「自己友」？只陳帆聲稱對姪女的申請、遴選均不知情，云云。其他傳媒也不報。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆是民望甚低之官員，卻為林鄭妹仔忠僕，沙中線醜聞、一地兩檢、港鐵變黨鐵配合圍捕示威者，有實無名的宵禁&hellip;&hellip;都有一份。雖庸才一事無成，但朝中有人好做官，難怪有人質疑叔姪私相授受，背後發功。<br />\n<br />\n當然這沒證據，而政府任何運作都不公平不公正不公義不公開，滿手鮮血也滿身錢腥，順者受惠，逆者受死。習慣了，竟全不避嫌，亦無忌諱。大家見到不少官二代、紅二代、富二代、星二代，靠人事、後台、裙帶關係扶植上位，一望即知是「阿斗」，但爛泥也得扶上壁，組成後援隊鞏固勢力，「攀親帶故」好平常，別當一回事。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"e9db57072e0c9a77a248a849f3e93bf6b311083e","tid":1800233,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:14:22.000Z","msg":"借個位，近期聯署：<br />\n(1) 美國白宮，取消北京冬奧<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/U5fLNAqmw2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FU5fLNAqmw2&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=24cdd157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/U5fLNAqmw2</a><br />\n<br />\n(2)美國白宮，凍結奶共企業資產<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/MrlLtO7axR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMrlLtO7axR&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=9f39be1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/MrlLtO7axR</a><br />\n<br />\n(3)日本人權法<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/eKjuAU6v4I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeKjuAU6v4I&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=28d2fd79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/eKjuAU6v4I</a><br />\n<br />\n(4)德國人權法仲有3日咋, 現在還未夠1萬人，急急急，快簽<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/cnoSfbTV6T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcnoSfbTV6T&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=5088fb3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/cnoSfbTV6T</a><br />\n附教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/ZAF6HbpVJX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FZAF6HbpVJX&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=148cf534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/ZAF6HbpVJX</a>"},{"pid":"8622f2c0efb2cc204d6046de05a562631c154011","tid":1800233,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">和你坐  Stuck稅局</span><br />\n12月30日 星期一<br />\n時間 : 12:00<br />\n地點 : 稅務大樓<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: oran